parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS module can cause the ABS and brake lights to flash, leading to a loss of braking power, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ABS light flashes on and off
the brake light flashes on and off
and there is a loss of braking power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake booster can cause the brake pedal to become stiff or hard to press, leading to a loss of braking power, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal is stiff or hard to press
the brake pedal does not respond when depressed
and there is a loss of braking power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water ingress into the brake system can cause the brake booster to freeze, leading to a loss of braking power, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal is stiff or hard to press
the brake pedal does not respond when depressed
and there is a loss of braking power.
